# Google Place photos — image widget rule

- For **`Place.photos`**, Moody **`photo_url`**, or any `maps.googleapis.com/.../place/photo` URL from Explore / `places_cache` / My Day: use **`WmPlacePhotoNetworkImage`** (`lib/core/presentation/widgets/wm_network_image.dart`). Same pipeline everywhere (hero, list cards, grid, Foto’s, fullscreen).
- For avatars, Unsplash, social images, or other arbitrary HTTPS images: use **`WmNetworkImage`**.
- Do not use raw `Image.network` for Google place photos. Do not duplicate URL rewriting outside **`deviceAccessibleGooglePlacePhotoUrl`** / **`WmPlacePhotoNetworkImage`**.
